How to associate style information with the XML tag:
- We can give appearance to a XML file by adding a CSS style sheet using the following line in the XML file:
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" href="myFile.css"?>

- It is a type of processing instruction.
- Formatting XML with CSS is not recommended. Use JavaScript or XSLT instead.
Example: 02-Associating-XML-CSS project
